good doer
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:  1
Definition:a farm animal that converts feed to meat or milk readily or that performs well when put to test.


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
